Maintainer: File Organizer Team <team@fileorganizer.app>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, libayatana-appindicator3-1
Description: AI-powered local file organizer
 File Organizer is a privacy-first AI-powered local file management system.
 It organizes files intelligently using local LLMs with zero cloud dependencies.
 .
 Features include text, image, audio, and video file processing with AI analysis,
 smart file organization suggestions, and a terminal user interface.
